Alien Assault Traders - Readme

A web-based massively multi-player strategy game of space trading and combat.

Version 0.13
http://www.aatraders.com

This program is free software; you can redistribute it and/or modify it under 
the terms of the GNU Public License (see LICENSE or 
http://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl.html)

This program is distributed in the hope that it will be useful,
but WITHOUT ANY WARRANTY; without even the implied warranty of
MERCHANTABILITY or FITNESS FOR A PARTICULAR PURPOSE.  See the GNU Public
License for more details.

Requirements: 
    PHP4.3.0 or higher (tested with 4.3.2)
    MySQL (tested with 4.0.3 recommend 4.0.3 or higher)
    ADODB (included 4.03)
    Smarty (included 2.5)

Download:
    You can get the newest version at http://www.aatraders.com

Credits:
    Alien Assault Traders is based off of the original BlackNova Traders and Nova Gaming System code 
    (specifically the .54 release of NGS). Their CHANGELOG information can be found in their project files.

Installation:
    Please see the INSTALL file.

ChangeLog:
    Please see the CHANGES file.    

Documentation:
    None to speak of yet.

Updates:
    Join the forums at http://www.aatraders.com .

Enjoy,


